{"id": "1232023026480971860", "channel_id": "1231285533909454991", "type": 0, "author_id": "968857106985910302", "author_name": "enosred", "author_bot": false, "content": "只算常驻的话这么几种配队：混沌盾击反击、深海水母毒、血肉尤乌或者希洛打击队、超维的栗子队伍。", "timestamp": "2024-04-22T17:39:39.394000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1231285533909454991", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "入坑一个月了还是不知道应该抽什么角色好", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1232023718080024596", "channel_id": "1231285533909454991", "type": 0, "author_id": "968857106985910302", "author_name": "enosred", "author_bot": false, "content": "你后面需要打无光和融灾，每次的活动成就也需要你打一遍每个界域。所以最后每个界域你还是都需要练的（", "timestamp": "2024-04-22T17:42:24.284000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1231285533909454991", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "入坑一个月了还是不知道应该抽什么角色好", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1232024781457461248", "channel_id": "1231285533909454991", "type": 0, "author_id": "968857106985910302", "author_name": "enosred", "author_bot": false, "content": "抽卡建议的话现在是血肉神父和深海图鲁的池子准备关了，图鲁可以抽一只备用。后面是混沌24和超维福袋，24要是技能组强可以抽，福袋的话因为你超维基本抽满了要是歪了收益很低可以放着。", "timestamp": "2024-04-22T17:46:37.813000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1231285533909454991", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "入坑一个月了还是不知道应该抽什么角色好", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1232025323676369028", "channel_id": "1231285533909454991", "type": 0, "author_id": "968857106985910302", "author_name": "enosred", "author_bot": false, "content": "再后面的话复刻是红夫人和莉莉，红夫人强度算正常，莉莉抽一只。不过后面up的限定强度也不低。到时候你基本玩得也够久了，更喜欢哪个界域看自己情况抽取。", "timestamp": "2024-04-22T17:48:47.088000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1231285533909454991", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "入坑一个月了还是不知道应该抽什么角色好", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
